  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046370/extras/99e9d30341284641424d69e3f47497fc.avif?t=1563182076\" width=460 height=215 /></span><br>Meaty McSkinBones is a single-player puzzle/platformer where the character is split into three separate bodies. They each have unique abilities or can work together to solve puzzles and traverse the environment. It's quirky, hilarious, and a ton of fun!<br><br>Key Features:<br>- Over 14 unique, challenging levels<br>- Character-to-character 'interaction' mechanics where the characters work together<br>- A charming, engrossing story<br>- A hilariously gross, quirky, cheesy aesthetic",
